Horde
-----

The Webmail Groupware product that is included with Exim4U is a modified
version of the Horde Groupware Webmail Edition product which has been
pre-configured to work seamlessly with your Exim4U installation. The 
The Horde applications are free software provided under the GNU Library
General Public License, Version 2, dated June 1991 which is described here:

http://www.horde.org/licenses/lgpl.php

